    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img class="left" src="/images/articles/writing.jpg" width="260"></p>

<p>I haven't spent much time writing content for this blog, but I have been doing some writing on other sites. Here are some of my posts from other sites:</p>

<!-- more -->


<ul>
<li><a href="http://concordantsolutions.com/4-techniques-developing-ios-android/">4 Techniques for Developing for both iOS and Android</a> Discusses the pros and cons of web apps vs. native apps vs. cross compiling tools such as Titanium</li>
<li><a href="http://concordantsolutions.com/the-value-in-launching-early/">The Value in Launching Early</a> Why pushing your launch date up by cutting features is only going to make you more money.</li>
<li><a href="http://concordantsolutions.com/dont-bill-hourly/">Why We Don't Bill Hourly</a> An explination of my logic behind changing my billing techniques in 2014. Protip: Start billing weekly.</li>
<li><a href="http://concordantsolutions.com/aarrr-pirate-metrics-5-numbers-you-need-to-know-about-your-business/">Pirate Metrics, 5 Numbers you Need to Know About Your Business</a>. Writing about the main metrics companies should be looking at.</li>
<li><a href="https://medium.com/p/6c9c9f08b552">How Letting Go of Money Made me More of It</a> One of my personal favorites. Discussing how life lessons from being a profressional online poker player translate into being a consultant.</li>
</ul>


